## 激活条件
- 判断逻辑: 距离等级从解锁圈内变为迎宾圈外（`distanceLevel >= PLBLEKeyDistanceLevelWelcomeCircle`）
- 代码位置: PLXPPollingFirstPollingHandler.mm:137
- 锚点签名: `self.distanceLevel >= PLBLEKeyDistanceLevelWelcomeCircle`
- 日志关键字: [kBLEKeyPollingTag] `PLogic` 相关日志
- 说明: 距离预测算法（BLELocation）周期性计算 RSSI → 距离等级，当等级穿过迎宾圈时调用 predictLock

## 调用链
```
[1] BLELocation 距离预测引擎输出 distanceLevel 变化
    ├─ 代码: PLXPBleLocationManager → 定位处理器 → 回调 distanceLevel
    ├─ 说明: RSSI 信号 → KNN/一代/二代预测算法 → 距离等级
    └─ 输出: distanceLevel (PLBLEKeyDistanceLevel 枚举)

[2] PollingHandler 检测到 distanceLevel >= WelcomeCircle
    ├─ 代码: PLXPPollingFirstPollingHandler.mm:117, _handleLocationResult:
    ├─ 锚点签名: `self.distanceLevel >= PLBLEKeyDistanceLevelWelcomeCircle`
    ├─ 日志: [kBLEKeyPollingTag]
    └─ 输出: 调用 predictLock

[3] predictLock 执行闭锁判断
    ├─ 代码: PLXPPollingFirstPollingHandler.mm:149, predictLock
    ├─ 锚点签名: `self.operateNativeUnlockInLockRange`
    ├─ 日志: [kBLEKeyPollingTag] `PLogic，操作了主动解锁，不闭锁`（若拦截）
    └─ 输出: 调用 delegate.pollingLockIfNeed: → delegate.sendPollingLockCommand:

[4] pollingLockIfNeed: 多条件校验
    ├─ 代码: PLXPPollingManager.mm:948, pollingLockIfNeed:
    ├─ 锚点签名: `self.isDoorOpen`
    ├─ 日志: [kBLEKeyPollingTag] `启用的mode1,不做闭锁` / `车辆是开门状态` / `超过3次`
    └─ 输出: YES/NO

[5] sendPollingLockCommand: 发送闭锁指令
    ├─ 代码: PLXPPollingManager.mm:868, sendPollingLockCommand:
    ├─ 锚点签名: `bleConnectState == XPBLEConnectionStateAvailable`
    ├─ 日志: [kBLEKeyPollingTag] `<PA>主蓝牙连接-鉴权成功，发送闭锁指令` / `<PA>主蓝牙连接-鉴权失败，发送4G上锁`
    ├─ 分支: BLE 已鉴权 → sendPollingBussinessCommand:XPPollingBussinessPollingLock
    ├─ 分支: BLE 未鉴权 → sendPollingBussinessCommand:XPPollingBussiness4GRevertLock
    └─ 输出: → [6]

[6] sendPollingBussinessCommand → sendLockCommand（跨模块边界）
    ├─ 代码: PLXPPollingManager.mm:454, case XPPollingBussinessPollingLock → sendLockCommand
    ├─ 锚点签名: `[self sendLockCommand]`
    ├─ 日志: [kBLEKeyPollingTag] `<PA>发送Polling上锁指令`
    ├─ sendLockCommand 内部:
    │   ├─ ALL_WORK_KEY_EXIST 分支 → sendAllWorkCommand:PLXPTBoxCommandPollingLock
    │   └─ 默认分支 → PLXPCommandTool.sendCommand:XPVehicleCommandPollingLock
    ├─ 跨模块入口: XPVehicleSDK.shared.vehicleManager.currentVehicle sendCommand:cmd success: failed:
    ├─ 入参: XPVehicleCommandPollingLock（枚举值）
    ├─ 期望回调: success → pollingLockResultWithIsSuccess:YES + 播放声音/震动 + postAutoLockNotificationWithLockSuccess:YES
    ├─ 失败回调: failed → XPVehicleError; channel==TCP 时为 HTTP 失败 → pollingLockResultWithIsSuccess:NO + postAutoLockNotificationWithLockSuccess:NO
    └─ @ref(module:XPVehicleSDK, node:polling-command-dispatch) [待创建]
